Wednesday, September 7, 1994

MERIT DOCKET

94-1042. State ex rel. Cheren v. Zaleski.

Summit County, No. 16458. Sua sponte, cause dismissed and motion to strike overruled.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., dissents and would affirm.
